This app is the culmination of what’s wrong with the world.  If you want to know why people are unhappy with America, install this app.  Not only is the hentai on this app censored, but the storylines are flimsy and the character development is minimal if any.  A question that often came to mind while browsing through this app was “Does the creator of this have a hitler fetish?” this is something I am sure many people, not just me, found themselves questioning.  If I could give this zero stars, I would.

attributes.title: scam. no cheetos available
attributes.review: i downloaded this app because i was excited to be receiving my monthly subscription of cheeto puffs. i thought what a great idea for someone to make a subscription of this! WRONG! this app was totally misleading and did not satisfy me in the slightest 😡 when i first downloaded it, i was brought to a page full of trumps face covered in cheeto puff dust! i thought this was weird, but i thought maybe it was some sort of weird marketing for cheetos. however, the app kept glitching and bringing me to really weird websites, ones i found inappropriate. clearly this is a very poorly assembled website, i’m sure it was put together by a smart squirrel. every time i tried to exit the website, it would glitch and bring me back to it, making it extremely hard to even go on with my day! whenever i tried to close the app, it wouldn’t let me until i completed some task it was asking me to do, such as sign a petition or text a word to a number. clearly this is very trashy and inconsiderate, as well as inconvenient. do not download this app please!!! you will be wasting your time and you will have to jump through hoops to even close it, and you won’t even get your monthly cheeto puffs!! SCAM SCAM SCAM DO NOT DOWNLOAD!!
